        <Parent_String>building plans by column layouts [300135989], building plan attributes [300121970], form attributes for architecture [300226843], form attributes [300226816], attributes and properties by specific type [300226808], Attributes and Properties (hierarchy name) [300123559], Physical Attributes Facet [300264087]</Parent_String>
